<i>noun</i>: 구김새 [구김새] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>구김새 [구김새]</dt><br>
<dd>1. wrinkles; creases; folds</dd><br>
<dd>종이나 천 등이 구겨진 정도나 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>The extent or appearance of paper or cloth being crumpled.</dd><br>
<dd>2. low spirit; discouragement</dd><br>
<dd>기가 꺾이거나 풀이 죽은 태도나 얼굴빛.</dd><br>
<dd>One's attitude or look indicating that one is discouraged or in low spirit.</dd><br>
<dd>3. halt; pause; stammering</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 글이 이치에 닿지 않아 막히는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>The manner in which one's words or writing does not make sense without failing to continue.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>